creator: Tapkey
descriptionHtml:
Tapkey turns your smartphone into a super-secure key. Combined with Tapkey-enabled locking devices, the app allows you to open entrance doors, shared office spaces, lockers, garage doors and cars with your smartphone. In addition, you can grant access to others and track locking activities. Access management has never been that easy!

Features

- Secure sign-on: with your Google Account or Tapkey ID
- Register locking devices: with the app
- Easy access management: grant and remove access at any time
- Keyring: all access authorizations at a glance
- Open smart locks: with the NFC (Near Field) and/or BLE (Bluetooth Low Energy) functionality of your smartphone—no internet connection required
- Use NFC transponders: as alternative access medium that can directly be programmed with NFC-enabled smartphones
- Check locking activities: in the access log of the Tapkey app
- High security standards: comparable to online banking with strong cryptography and firmware updates directly via your smartphone

Locking Devices

Tapkey-enabled products can be ordered at https://shop.tapkey.com, Amazon or our partner's dealer network.
descriptionShort: Tapkey turns your smartphone into a super-secure key for all kind of locks.

title: Tapkey

creator: Tapkey
descriptionHtml:
The Tapkey app enables you to unlock Tapkey-compatible lock products (from different hardware partners) such as cylinders, wall readers, padlocks, escutcheons and furniture locks fast and securely using your smartphone. In addition, lock owners can register locks, issue, restrict and revoke smartphone keys, and also write NFC transponders.

Access management has never been that easy!

Tapkey Functions at a Glance
- Open smart locks with your mobile phone or NFC transponder
- Use NFC and BLE technology—no internet connection is required
- Issue an unlimited number of smartphone keys
- Set time restrictions and instantly revoke access rights
- Activate and update locks with the app
- See the access protocol
- Register securely with your Google, Apple or Tapkey ID

Your Advantages
- Easy management: Offer instant access with Tapkey. Time-consuming key handovers are no longer needed.
- Smart usage: No further products such as a bridge are required. Smart locks can be unlocked without internet connection.
- Flexible application: Combine different form factors (cylinders, wall readers, padlocks, escutcheons and furniture locks) for your specific use case.

Tapkey-compatible Locks
Are you interested in Tapkey and looking for the right hardware? Then visit our online store at https://tapkey.com/pages/shop, Amazon store or contact a local DOM dealer.

User Pricing
Our user pricing depends on the number of smartphone users. You can purchase up to 250 access permissions directly in the app. Furthermore, we offer individual packages upon request.
descriptionShort: The Smart Keyring for Tapkey-compatible Locks

title: Tapkey

creator: Tapkey
descriptionHtml:
The Tapkey app enables you to unlock Tapkey-compatible lock products (from different hardware partners) such as cylinders, wall readers, padlocks, escutcheons and furniture locks fast and securely using your smartphone. In addition, lock owners can register locks, issue, restrict and revoke smartphone keys, and also write NFC transponders.

Access management has never been that easy!

Tapkey Functions at a Glance
- Open smart locks with your mobile phone or NFC transponder
- Use NFC and BLE technology—no internet connection is required
- Issue an unlimited number of smartphone keys
- Set time restrictions and instantly revoke access rights
- Activate and update locks with the app
- See the access protocol
- Register securely with your Google, Apple or Tapkey ID

Your Advantages
- Easy management: Offer instant access with Tapkey. Time-consuming key handovers are no longer needed.
- Smart usage: No further products such as a bridge are required. Smart locks can be unlocked without internet connection.
- Flexible application: Combine different form factors (cylinders, wall readers, padlocks, escutcheons and furniture locks) for your specific use case.

Tapkey-compatible Locks
Are you interested in Tapkey and looking for the right hardware? Then visit our online store at https://tapkey.com/pages/shop, Amazon store or contact a local DOM dealer.

User Pricing
Our user pricing depends on the number of smartphone users. You can purchase up to 250 access permissions directly in the app. Furthermore, we offer individual packages upon request.
descriptionShort: The Smart Keyring for Tapkey-compatible Locks
